nput-search/Search/组件属性.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": \"harmonyos-6.1-8k\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"article\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"doc_id\": \"doc.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-text-input-search-search-2\",\r\n      \"title\": \"组件事件\",\r\n      \"score\": 267.523,\r\n      \"summary\": \"public func onSubmit(callback: ?(String) -> Unit): This **功能：** 点击搜索图标、搜索按钮或者按下软键盘搜索按钮时触发该事件。 **系统能力：** SystemCapability.ArkUI.ArkUI.Full **起始版本：** 22 **参数：** public func onChange(callback: ?(String) -> Unit): This\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-text-input-search/Search/组件事件.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": \"harmonyos-6.1-8k\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"article\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"doc_id\": \"doc.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-text-input-search-search-overview\",\r\n      \"title\": \"Search\",\r\n      \"score\": 266.455,\r\n      \"summary\": \"本目录包含基于仓颉语言的ArkUI框架Search组件API参考文档。内容涵盖了组件的初始化方法、SearchController控制器定义、用户交互事件处理（如提交、复制、粘贴）以及组件属性配置（如占位符、字体、搜索按钮）。该文档适用于ArkUI应用开发者，旨在帮助开发者构建功能完善、交互丰富的搜索输入界面，支持从基础创建到高级光标控制及外观定制的全流程开发。\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-text-input-search/Search/.overview.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": \"harmonyos-6.1-8k\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"overview\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"doc_id\": \"doc.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-text-input-search-search-abstract\",\r\n      \"title\": \".abstract\",\r\n      \"score\": 264.692,\r\n      \"summary\": \"本目录包含基于仓颉语言的ArkUI框架Search组件API参考文档。内容涵盖了组件的初始化方法、SearchController控制器定义、用户交互事件处理（如提交、复制、粘贴）以及组件属性配置（如占位符、字体、搜索按钮）。该文档适用于ArkUI应用开发者，旨在帮助开发者构建功能完善、交互丰富的搜索输入界面，支持从基础创建到高级光标控制及外观定制的全流程开发。\",\r\n      \"paths\": [\r\n        \"harmonyos-6.1-8k/API/arkui-cj/cj-text-input-search/Search/.abstract.md\"\r\n      ],\r\n      \"source\": \"harmonyos-6.1-8k\",\r\n      \"doc_kind\": \"abstract\"\r\n    },\r\n    {\r\n      \"doc_id\": \"doc.harmonyos-6-1-8k-api-arkui-cj-cj-text-input-search-search